name: Sandwhirl
Lore: 'Jawa shamans often predict when and where a sandstorm is going to take place. Even when caught in such a storm, the Jawas know how to avoid misfortune.',
Text: 'Deploy on a Desert. Specify starting direction. All characters (except Jawas and Tusken Raiders) present at same non-interior site are missing. During your control phase, moves to next adjacent site (reversing directions as necessary), but lost if at an interior site.',
